<item>
            <title>[SWF-1389] MessageContextErrors doesn&apos;t obey the Errors contract</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SWF-1389</link>
                <project id="10050" key="SWF">Spring Web Flow</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;As explained in the above forum thread, &lt;tt&gt;MessageContextErrors&lt;/tt&gt; throws a runtime exception when any class-level JSR-303 @Constraints are violated. The bug is in the &lt;tt&gt;rejectValue&lt;/tt&gt; method:&lt;/p&gt;

